Sound Recording Log. Collected by Paul Grose. Compositions for a music literacy
              class hosted by Vida Chenoweth and students. Papua New Guinea, North Solomons,
              Rotokas. 7/8/1986.

Kaarite. Kaagu. Contents: Port Moresby Lae (rainbow); Ukarumpa Land Rover to
              Kaagu; Bee returns after 3 years; Bee, Vida, Usarufas opening of Gadsup
              Council; Sing-Sing Kaagu; house building; making string bags; women gardening;
              road work; children; Kaarite; carrying Bee and pig; coffee skit of yaws; mock
              fight with shields; fence building; house building; child getting bath;
              roofing; children's play; melodica for transcribing (and "twinkle").
